  <brief_title>Effect of Postoperative Immobilization on Healing After Rotator Cuff Arthroscopic Repair</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Postoperative Immobilization on Healing After Rotator Cuff Arthroscopic Repair With Double Row Technique in Small or Medium Ruptures. Prospective, Comparative and Randomized.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
