    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to establish whether one month postoperative immobilization compared early
      passive motion after rotator cuff arthroscopic repair in small or medium ruptures with double
      row technique has any healing significance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
